"USAGE
  ib dev feedback get <id> [flags]

DESCRIPTION
  Fetch one feedback row by id (developer-only).
  Permissions: requires isSystemAdmin or isDeveloper.

ARGUMENTS
  <id> NUMBER    feedbackId (required)

FLAGS
